name: .QUICKENDATA File Extension
type_name: Quicken Essentials for Mac Data File
summary: Learn about .QUICKENDATA files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Financial data format used by Quicken Essentials for Mac, the Mac OS X version of the Quicken personal financial management software; saves financial data for the user, such as account, loan, investment, and transaction information.

content: NOTE: The Windows version of Quicken uses the .QDF format for user financial data.
